'''Maruyama Kofun''' (円山古墳)

* {{ill|Maruyama Kofun (Yasu)|ja|円山古墳 (野洲市)}} - A kofun located in Yasu City, Shiga Prefecture. Part of the National Historic Site "Ōiwayama Kofun Group."
* {{ill|Maruyama Kofun (Kyoto)|ja|円山古墳 (京都市)}} - A kofun located in Kyoto City, Kyoto Prefecture. Designated as "Maruyama Mausoleum Reference Site" by the Imperial Household Agency.
* {{ill|Kisaichi Maruyama Kofun|ja|私市円山古墳}} - A kofun located in Ayabe City, Kyoto Prefecture. A National Historic Site.

{{aimai}}
